{"name":"Army of One (Magic-User Level 3)","type":"spell","img":"/systems/lotfp/assets/default/spell.png","data":{"lvl":3,"class":"Magic-User","duration":"1 Round/level","range":"Touch","roll":"","description":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The recipient of this spell becomes a peerless warrior, able to move in battle with inhuman reflexes in order to attack enemies within immediate m&ecirc;l&eacute;e range. The subject is able to make one m&ecirc;l&eacute;e attack for every opponent already engaging him. Each attack must be against a different opponent, and the extra attacks are not gained if the subject must move to engage a foe.&nbsp;</p>","memorized":0,"cast":0,"save":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"StAYtEi0AtlPHrBE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.5RXhGJf8eWmtSmHk"}},"_id":"X762Vwgt1H3MPPPY"}
{"_id":"XRTyvqpShnel6GGT","name":"Speak with Animals (Magic-User Level 2)","type":"spell","img":"/systems/lotfp/assets/default/spell.png","data":{"lvl":2,"class":"Magic-User","duration":"2 Rounds/level","range":"0","roll":"","description":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The caster can comprehend and communicate with ordinary animals or giant versions of ordinary animals. The caster can ask questions of, and receive answers from, one particular kind of animal, although the spell does not make it any more friendly or cooperative than normal. The type of animal is decided when the spell is cast. If an animal is friendly toward the caster, it may do him some favor or service.</p>","memorized":0,"cast":0,"save":""},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"StAYtEi0AtlPHrBE":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.tmANWNHmunbRLBZU"}}}
